{"tid":1716522,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"關於中環black bloc 問題, 歡迎入黎討論","createTime":"2019-11-13T11:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T13:54:49.000Z","uid":61690,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"282948ef5e0424736639dfcf71d572959325719d","tid":1716522,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:03:12.000Z","msg":"命題: 中環中午和你lunch呢d快閃活動，應唔應該black bloc?<br />\n<br />\n企得前+set rb + 作戰緊 black bloc當然發揮到佢既用途<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係</span></span><br />\n作戰前black bloc反而會令你好危險, 去緊/離開/圍觀 應該行街look, 越斯文斯好<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">正如好多人講, 搵個影唔到既位加件外套變色啦! 附近好多唔同裝束既人cover你</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">正確用盡black bloc既方法係黑底衫，帶件全衣櫃最斯文既外套。要做野先搵暗位 小隊傘陣變裝，做完野再變返路人甲。</span></span><br />\n歡迎討論，我會睇曬大家既comment再做總結。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提一提:<br />\n有d手足明明見畜龍係附近捉緊人, 仲全身black bloc圍觀, 我個人認為好不智, 佢可以即場禁底你，明知自己black bloc就唔好留係戰場,要圍觀變左裝先準你圍<br />\n<br />\n大家要以智取勝，諗下有咩方法令自己最少時間係black bloc"},{"pid":"d7a0eccc90d51c637054d2246cc9756993b8a9ed","tid":1716522,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:04:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a5e41dead3277454e34a2231f690191054962eaf","tid":1716522,"uid":266212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"我都同意，活用black bloc，街坊變身"},{"pid":"45ca4fe7339988f3d629c137ef6fad08092506c7","tid":1716522,"uid":266212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:04:56.000Z","msg":"中環啲細街無咩cam"},{"pid":"5ba9a96eb30e713da45af2d9a88d55628bf11805","tid":1716522,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:07:08.000Z","msg":"正確用盡black bloc既方法係黑底衫，帶件全衣櫃最斯文既外套。要做野先搵暗位 小隊傘陣變裝，做完野再變返路人甲"},{"pid":"734b39eac19a97234740f1db1fd10164c241203e","tid":1716522,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"